  "text": "25th March, 2004 Notification No. 43/2004 - Custom (N.T) In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-section (1) of section 4 of the Customs Act, 1962 (52 of 1962), the Central Board of Excise and Customs hereby appoints the Commissioner of Customs (Imports), Air Cargo Complex ,Sahar Airport , Mumbai to act as Commissioner of Customs, Bangalore for the purposes of adjudicating the matters relating to Show Cause Notices pertaining to M/s. Nanoli Stud Farm, Himalaya House, 5th Floor, D.N.Road, Mumbai-1, M/s Highgrove Stud Farm, , Himalaya House, 5th Floor, D.N.Road, Mumbai-1, and M/s Five Star Shipping Co. Pvt. Limited, Himalaya House, 5th Floor, D.N.Road, Mumbai-1 issued vide DRI/BZU/E/8/2003/8822 to 8829, dated the 20thNovember,2003 by the Additional Director General, Directorate of Revenue Intelligence, Mumbai. D.S.Garbyal Under Secretary to the Government of India F.NO.437/25/2003-CUS.IV -- 1 of 1 --",
